==English==

===Noun===
'''[[desert]] [[soil]]'''

# A [[soil]] variety typically found in [[arid]] climates, usually with little [[leach]]ing and minimal [[humus]] content. Referred to as an "aridisol" in the [[nomenclature]] of the United States Department of Agriculture's Natural Resources Conservation Service.

